=========================
grammar with metavars
=========================

metavar a {{ tex \alpha }}, b, c ::=
indexvar i, j ::=

grammar

type, t :: 'ty_' ::=
  | a                   ::  :: var
  | </ ti // -> // i /> ::  :: arrow
---
